### Submit Certification Request (Sitter)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/certifications/submit
Authorization: Bearer {sitter_token}

### Get Pending Certifications (Admin Only)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/certifications/pending
Authorization: Bearer {admin_token}

### Approve Certification (Admin Only)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/certifications/approve
Authorization: Bearer {admin_token}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "requestId": 1
}

### Reject Certification (Admin Only)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/certifications/reject
Authorization: Bearer {admin_token}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "requestId": 1
}

### Check Certification Status (Public)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/certifications/status/2

